=== Plasma

(((Plasma)))
Plasma is a group on https://invent.kde.org[Invent] with many different projects that deal with the graphical workspaces environment or User interface(UI). It describes the group as:

Desktop environment for a wide range of devices and user needs:

==== Plasma Projects

(((Plasma, Projects)))
The top three Plasma projects are:

https://invent.kde.org/plasma/kwin[KWin] - Easy to use, but flexible, X Window Manager and Wayland Compositor

https://invent.kde.org/plasma/plasma-desktop[plasma-desktop] - Plasma for the Desktop

https://invent.kde.org/plasma/plasma-workspace[plasma-workspace] - Various components needed to run a Plasma-based environment

For more Plasma Projects see:

https://invent.kde.org/plasma[invent.kde.org/plasma]